{"tid":779480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美空軍傳將採購新型F-15X戰機 掛22枚飛彈變「飛行武器庫」","createTime":"2018-08-14T12:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T02:05:51.000Z","uid":141151,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7d7e2d5bff8745c3961d2afca817326165996366","tid":779480,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"美空軍傳將採購新型F-15X戰機 掛22枚飛彈變「飛行武器庫」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2506718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2506718&d=DrYW53ZiRSe9wNmx%2B8wU6ttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=510c91cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2506718&h=461873f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2506718</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國空軍傳出將向波音公司採購名為「F-15X」的新型F-15戰機，F-15X採用新型掛架系統，可搭載更多武裝，屆時F-15X上可以掛載22枚空對空飛彈，宛如「飛行武器庫」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，F-15在1970年代推出，服役至今已有40幾年，且不管是空對空或是空對地打擊任務都能勝任。而美國空軍採購新型的F-15X的目的則在於紓解F-22猛禽戰機的服役壓力以及F-35戰機的緩慢生產，加上過去各界曾經質疑F-35的功能性，質疑F-35在空中纏鬥和近距離空中支援上，是否能分別勝過F-15戰機和A-10攻擊機，F-15X未來服役後將能彌補F-35的不足之處。<br />\n<br />\nF-15X針對性能做出提升，採用新型武器掛架系統，可搭載更多武裝，最多可掛載22枚空對空飛彈，或是8枚空對空飛彈搭配7枚2000磅重的炸彈，加上升級的電戰套件以及電子掃描陣列雷達。<br />\n<br />\n另外，F-15X的使用成本也比其他戰機低，F-15X每小時飛行費用約為2萬7000美元，比F-35A每小時超過4萬美元的飛行成本低上不少，而在F-15X服役後，將有2萬小時的使用壽命，這意味著F-15X可以服役數十年之久。<br />\n<br />\n針對美國空軍將採購新型F-15X的傳聞，波音公司高層則是尚未證實此事，空軍官員則表示「沒有收購計畫」，無法對此事做出評論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1b7e2d8e397beccf3676de28d8d9f99f264e9c","tid":779480,"uid":5490,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"一架22支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cbeac5810dd0a71cc0a1605173c56703b28ca8","tid":779480,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0b759ffec1c6e31b403d57f4e8a094e8128b59","tid":779480,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:32:21.000Z","msg":"彈幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9e437169034ad7ffdaf90fd4282db36a90c12b","tid":779480,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:39:58.000Z","msg":"要做導彈卡車，咁俾埋AI自己揸算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baabebdc34193d10cfb20fcb659dd2bece3cb581","tid":779480,"uid":40216,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:56:46.000Z","msg":"Ace combat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e211be78f9e54043262f9b2c9f8afac12d3599","tid":779480,"uid":62532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"變戰機game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f8d653ac13aeaf1f76b4a6b1b725c30a7c7995","tid":779480,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>傳</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc050431580b9f5ca6050f847e43334afd1ccab","tid":779480,"uid":35656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"掛個貨櫃上戰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964eeb8ca081efa95e2382b4d3517a7272673738","tid":779480,"uid":76216,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:09:46.000Z"